de.lmu.ifi.dbs.elki.index.tree.metrical.mtreevariants.mktrees.mkmax

Class MkMaxLeafEntry

  • java.lang.Object
    • de.lmu.ifi.dbs.elki.index.tree.AbstractLeafEntry
      • de.lmu.ifi.dbs.elki.index.tree.metrical.mtreevariants.MTreeLeafEntry
        • de.lmu.ifi.dbs.elki.index.tree.metrical.mtreevariants.mktrees.mkmax.MkMaxLeafEntry
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Entry, LeafEntry, MkMaxEntry, MTreeEntry, Externalizable, Serializable

    class MkMaxLeafEntry
extends MTreeLeafEntry
implements MkMaxEntry
    Represents an entry in a leaf node of an MkMaxTree. Additionally to an MTreeLeafEntry an MkMaxLeafEntry holds the k-nearest neighbor distance of the underlying data object.
    Author:
    Elke Achtert
